# Phosphor Icons

- Use `com.coffeepeek.admin.ui.icons.CpIcons` for all Compose UI icons.
- Do not import `androidx.compose.material.icons.*` or use `Icons.*`.
- If a new icon is needed, add a semantic property to `CpIcons` backed by `PhosphorIcons.Regular` or `PhosphorIcons.Fill`.
- Keep UI files independent from the raw Phosphor package so icon style changes stay centralized.
